entry.title: Combined summary - Bitcoin 0.10.0c1 available for download
entry.summary: Bitcoin.org has made the release candidate 1 of version 0.10.0 of Bitcoin available for download. Interested users can test the new release by downloading the binaries from the website. The preliminary release notes, which provide detailed information about the changes made and new features added in this version, are available on Github. Users are encouraged to report any bugs encountered while using the new release via the issue tracker on Github.
